data.title: Secretary Clinton Poses for a Photo With Slovakian Foreign Minister Dzurinda
data.meta_description: U.S. Secretary of State Hillary Rodham Clinton poses for a photo with Slovakian Foreign Minister Mikulas Dzurinda at the U.S. Department of State in Washington, D.C., on October 19, 2010. [State Department photo/ Public Domain]
